com.mysema.query
Interface Query<SubType extends Query<SubType>>

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractSQLQuery, OracleQuery, QueryAdapter, SQLQuery, SubQuery
public interface Query<SubType extends Query<SubType>>

Query provides a query interface of the fluent query DSL. Querydsl query implementations can be based also on other interfaces, but the signature should be a subset of Query.
